M|Reac|> **|**
M|Reac|tx|> This document is mainly for ag and LLMs to follow when maintaining,
M|Reac|tx|> generating, or refactoring rc and nx.js codebases. Humans
M|Reac|tx|> may also find it useful, but guidance here is optimized for automation
M|Reac|tx|> and consistency by AI-assisted workflows.
M|Reac|tx|---
M|Abst|tx|Comprehensive perf op guide for rc and nx.js applications, designed for AI ag and LLMs. Contains 40+ rules across 8 categories, prioritized by impact from ct (eliminating waterfalls, reducing bundle size) to incremental (advanced patterns). Each rule includes detailed explanations, real-world examples comparing incorrect vs. correct implementations, and specific impact metrics to guide automated refactoring and code generation.
