M|5.8 |**Im|md (avoids effect re-runs and duplicate side effects)**
M|5.8 |tx|If a side effect is triggered by a specific us action (submit, click, drag), run it in that event handler. Do not md the action as state + effect; it makes effects re-run on unrelated changes and can duplicate the action.
