M|5.9 |**Im|md (avoids recomputing independent steps)**
M|5.9 |tx|When a hook contains multiple independent tasks w/ different dependencies, split them into separate hooks. A combined hook reruns all tasks when any dependency changes, even if some tasks don't use the changed value.
