M|5.13|tx|const handler = () => setScrollY(window.scrollY)
M|5.13|wind|true })
M|5.13|tx|return () => window.removeEventListener('scroll', handler)
M|5.13|tx|}, [])
M|5.13|tx|}
M|5.13|tx|```
M|5.13|**Co|non-blocking updates**
M|5.13|tx|```tsx
