M|5.14|**Im|md (keeps input responsive during heavy computation)**
M|5.14|tx|When us input triggers expensive computations or renders, use `useDeferredValue` to keep the input responsive. The deferred value lags behind, allowing rc to prioritize the input up and render the expensive result when idle.
M|5.14|**In|input feels laggy while filtering**
