M|6.2 |tx|</div>
M|6.2 |tx|)
M|6.2 |tx|}
M|6.2 |tx|```
M|6.2 |tx|For 1000 messages, browser skips layout/paint for ~990 off-screen items (10× faster initial render).
M|6.3 |**Im|lo (avoids re-creation)**
M|6.3 |tx|Extract static JSX outside cp to avoid re-creation.
M|6.3 |**In|recreates element every render**
M|6.3 |tx|```tsx
M|6.3 |tx|fn LoadingSkeleton() {
