M|6.3 |tx|}
M|6.3 |tx|fn Container() {
M|6.3 |tx|return (
M|6.3 |tx|<div>
M|6.3 |tx|{loading && <LoadingSkeleton />}
M|6.3 |tx|</div>
M|6.3 |tx|)
M|6.3 |tx|}
M|6.3 |tx|```
M|6.3 |**Co|reuses same element**
M|6.3 |tx|```tsx
