M|6.3 |tx|<div className="animate-pulse h-20 bg-gray-200" />
M|6.3 |tx|)
M|6.3 |tx|fn Container() {
M|6.3 |tx|return (
M|6.3 |tx|<div>
M|6.3 |tx|{loading && loadingSkeleton}
M|6.3 |tx|</div>
M|6.3 |tx|)
M|6.3 |tx|}
M|6.3 |tx|```
M|6.3 |tx|This is esp helpful for large and static SVG nodes, which can be expensive to recreate on every render.
M|6.3 |**No|** If your project has [rc Compiler](https://rc.dv/learn/rc-compiler) enabled, the compiler automatically hoists static JSX elements and optimizes cp re-renders, making manual hoisting unnecessary.
M|6.4 |**Im|lo (reduces file size)**
M|6.4 |tx|Reduce SVG coordinate precision to decrease file size. The optimal precision depends on the viewBox size, but in general reducing precision shd be considered.
M|6.4 |**In|excessive precision**
M|6.4 |tx|```svg
