M|6.4 |tx|npx svgo --precision=1 --multipass icon.svg
M|6.4 |tx|```
M|6.5 |**Im|md (avoids visual flicker and hydration er)**
M|6.5 |tx|When rendering cn that depends on client-side storage (localStorage, cookies), avoid both SSR breakage and post-hydration flickering by injecting a synchronous script that updates the DOM before rc hydrates.
M|6.5 |**In|breaks SSR**
M|6.5 |tx|```tsx
M|6.5 |func|{ children: ReactNode }) {
M|6.5 |tx|// localStorage is not available on server - throws er
M|6.5 |tx|const theme = localStorage.getItem('theme') \|\| 'light'
M|6.5 |tx|return (
M|6.5 |tx|<div className={theme}>
M|6.5 |tx|{children}
M|6.5 |tx|</div>
M|6.5 |tx|)
M|6.5 |tx|}
M|6.5 |tx|```
M|6.5 |tx|Server-side rendering will fail bc `localStorage` is undefined.
M|6.5 |**In|visual flickering**
M|6.5 |tx|```tsx
M|6.5 |func|{ children: ReactNode }) {
M|6.5 |tx|const [theme, setTheme] = useState('light')
M|6.5 |tx|useEffect(() => {
M|6.5 |tx|// Runs after hydration - causes visible flash
M|6.5 |tx|const stored = localStorage.getItem('theme')
M|6.5 |tx|if (stored) {
M|6.5 |tx|setTheme(stored)
M|6.5 |tx|}
M|6.5 |tx|}, [])
M|6.5 |tx|return (
M|6.5 |tx|<div className={theme}>
M|6.5 |tx|{children}
M|6.5 |tx|</div>
M|6.5 |tx|)
M|6.5 |tx|}
M|6.5 |tx|```
M|6.5 |tx|cp first renders w/ default value (`light`), then updates after hydration, causing a visible flash of incorrect cn.
M|6.5 |**Co|no flicker, no hydration mismatch**
M|6.5 |tx|```tsx
