M|7.3 |tx|const len = arr.length
M|7.3 |tx|for (let i = 0; i < len; i++) {
M|7.3 |tx|process(value)
M|7.3 |tx|}
M|7.3 |tx|```
M|7.4 |**Im|md (avoid redundant computation)**
M|7.4 |tx|Use a md-level Map to cache fn results when the same fn is called repeatedly w/ the same inputs during render.
M|7.4 |**In|redundant computation**
M|7.4 |tx|```ts
M|7.4 |func|{ projects: Project[] }) {
M|7.4 |tx|return (
M|7.4 |tx|<div>
M|7.4 |tx|{projects.map(project => {
M|7.4 |tx|// slugify() called 100+ times for same project names
M|7.4 |tx|const slug = slugify(project.name)
M|7.4 |tx|return <ProjectCard key={project.id} slug={slug} />
