M|7.5 |**Im|lo-md (reduces expensive I/O)**
M|7.5 |tx|`localStorage`, `sessionStorage`, and `document.cookie` are synchronous and expensive. Cache reads in memory.
M|7.5 |**In|reads storage on every call**
M|7.5 |tx|```ts
