M|7.5 |tx|```
M|7.5 |**Co|Map cache**
M|7.5 |tx|```ts
M|7.5 |tx|const storageCache = new Map<string, string \| null>()
M|7.5 |func|string) {
M|7.5 |tx|if (!storageCache.has(key)) {
M|7.5 |tx|storageCache.set(key, localStorage.getItem(key))
M|7.5 |tx|}
