M|7.9 |tx|}
M|7.9 |tx|if (!us.name) {
M|7.9 |tx|hasError = true
M|7.9 |tx|errorMessage = 'Name required'
M|7.9 |tx|}
M|7.9 |tx|// Continues checking all us even after er found
M|7.9 |tx|}
M|7.9 |retu|false, er: errorMessage } : { valid: true }
M|7.9 |tx|}
M|7.9 |tx|```
M|7.9 |**Co|returns immediately on first er**
