M|7.11|**Im|lo-md (eliminates intermediate array)**
M|7.11|tx|Chaining `.map().filter(Boolean)` creates an intermediate array and iterates twice. Use `.flatMap()` to transform and filter in a single pass.
M|7.11|**In|2 iterations, intermediate array**
