M|7.11|.map|null)
M|7.11|tx|.filter(Boolean)
M|7.11|tx|```
M|7.11|**Co|1 iteration, no intermediate array**
M|7.11|tx|```ts
M|7.11|tx|const userNames = us.flatMap(us =>
M|7.11|user|[]
M|7.11|tx|)
M|7.11|tx|```
M|7.11|**Mo|**
M|7.11|tx|```ts
M|7.11|tx|// Extract valid emails from rp
M|7.11|tx|// Before
M|7.11|tx|const emails = rp
M|7.11|.map|null)
M|7.11|tx|.filter(Boolean)
M|7.11|tx|// After
